data.description:
Desirable single story home in Maricopa, AZ. Built in 2019, this 4 bedroom 2 bath 2,336Sqft home features modern property renovations that include stainless steel appliances, updated flooring, and granite countertops. Home also has a spacious backyard that is a blank canvas for you to make your own. 
The Sorrento community features a beautiful park, splash pad, tennis court, basketball court, Pickleball court, walking paths, and grassy fields. Conveniently located near the heart of Maricopa with shopping, dining, and just minutes to Copper Sky Recreation Complex.
